fields.name: Facial Products
fields.description:
Washing your face is the most basic and essential step of any routine, 
Whether it's moisturiser, a face mask, cleansers or exfoliators we've got what you need to perfect your skincare routine.

fields.name: Body Care Products
fields.description: Pamper yourself from head to toe with our range of body care. From lotions and massage bars, to deodorants and foot care, give your body the care it deserves.

fields.name: Body mist spray
fields.description: Take a moment to slow down with our luxuriously textured bath and body products

fields.name: Body lotion
fields.description: Formulated with Prebiotic Colloidal Oatmeal*, its clinically proven, fast-absorbing formula locks-in moisture to help protect and nourish normal to dry skin. The formula preserves the skin’s natural microbiome for healthy looking and more resilient skin with improved moisture barrier from 1st use.

fields.name: Body Cleanser
fields.description: Take on the day with a zap of energy and a charge of hydration with the NEW Super Shower Power Body Cleanser, superpowered by 100% natural spearmint, rosemary and eucalyptus essential oils.

fields.name: Body Perfume
fields.description: You can choose a Victoria's Secret body spray according to your taste, whether you want something sweet, floral, or a bit more exotic.

fields.name: La Roche-Posay Facial Scrub
fields.description: Purify & exfoliate your skin texture with Ultra-Fine Scrub by La Roche-Posay - an exfoliator for sensitive skin developed without soap.

fields.name: The Ordinary Mask
fields.description: The Ordinary Salicylic Acid 2% Mask is a deep-cleansing, exfoliating face mask to clear blemishes and congested skin while restoring a radiant glow.

fields.name: Facial Skin Gel
fields.description: Introducing new Simple Water Boost Micellar Facial Gel Wash, a new generation facial gel cleanser with Micellar technology, infused with skin-essential minerals and plant extract, this formula delivers instant hydration AND gentle yet effective cleansing – perfect for even sensitive skin.

fields.name: Body Deodorant Spray
fields.description: La Roche-Posay 24h Physiological Deodorant Spray is a very effective physiological deodorant sensitive skin, which provides comfort and freshness.

fields.name: Body Bar Soap
fields.description: While ordinary soaps can strip skin of essential moisture, Dove Beauty Bar has mild cleansers to effectively wash away dirt and germs and care beautifully.

fields.name: Facial Roller
fields.description: Prized for its powerful properties, this luxurious Jade Roller is a skincare essential. Designed to aid lymphatic drainage, reduce puffiness and release tension in facial muscles. We suggest pairing the Jade Roller with our Skin Nutrients Facial Oil to ensure the Jade Roller glides across skin with ease whilst brightening the skin, helping to reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.

fields.name: Pixi Mask
fields.description: Product Description. Give your skin the amazing boost it needs with this exfoliating microfibre sheet mask with 5% glycolic acid, aloe Vera and ginseng.

fields.name: Body Scrub
fields.description: Enriched with jojoba oil, sweet almond oil and mineral-rich dead sea salt, this scrub offers gentle, yet effective, exfoliation. Your skin is left perfectly smooth and soft.

fields.name: Body Sunscreen
fields.description:
NIVEA SUN Protect & Moisture Sun Lotion SPF 50+ - Superior sun care for your skin
NIVEA's Moisturising Sun Lotion provides you with highly effective SPF 50+ protection against sunburn and sun-induced skin damage. Specially designed to care for your skin, Protect & Moisturise is a gentle soothing sun lotion that cares for all skin types.

fields.name: Facial Serum
fields.description:
Olay Regenerist Daily Regenerating Serum Smooths the look of fine lines & wrinkles & regenerates skin’s youthful look. -Delivers anti-ageing ingredients deep into the skin's surface. -Exfoliates, Smooths, Brightens. -Ultra-lightweight & fast-absorbing.
1st Use: Instantly skin is visibly smoothed; skin's texture is softened. Over time: Appearance of fine lines & wrinkles is visibly improved.

fields.name: Neutrogena Toner
fields.description: Achieve perfectly clean skin with the Neutrogena Visibly Clear Spot Proofing Purifying Toner; a potent formula that helps to combat and prevent breakouts.

fields.name: Facial Mist
fields.description:
Multi-purpose, hydrating face mist

Gives skin a healthy, dewy glow

Clarifying Thyme & Rejuvenating Rose

fields.name: Eye Mask
fields.description: Elemis Pro-Collagen Hydra Gel Eye Masks have been clinically proven to instantly reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. The eye masks have been formulated with Potent plankton extract, combined with the power of Padina Pavonica and chlorella to provide an instant skin-tightening effect, whilst hyaluronic acid hydrates the fragile eye area. Eyes are left feeling intensely moisturised, creating an instant smoother look.

fields.name: Body Buffer
fields.description: Hydrea London's Body Buffer - shower puff that aids a deep, polishing cleanse.

fields.name: Facial Cleanser
fields.description: Looking for an effective, gentle and hydrating cleanser? Garnier Micellar Cleansing Water gently removes up to 100% make-up and intensely cleanses skin of dirt, oil, SPF, pollution & dead skin cells - all in one step! Skin is left soothed and free of impurities, revealing healthy-looking skin.

fields.name: Body Cream
fields.description: Discover our body creams and gels, each formulated to leave your skin feeling smooth and hydrated. Look to Garnier's body care range to moisturise your skin.
